room_title: Escape room "The Recruit 2.0" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: I went to Escape Chambers with a group from the East South Des Moines Chamber and did "the recruit." It was lots of fun! I'm excited to try other rooms. This would be fun for a work outing or with friends.

room_title: Escape room "The Recruit 2.0" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: What a great time we had! Always fun to meet new folks and we worked as a team - and made it out in time! Way to go, Team Style!!
